<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 03:15:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>IDC 称，由于 iPhone 出货量下降，苹果将第一大手机制造商的位置拱手让给了三星</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-loses-top-phonemaker-spot-samsung-iphone-shipments-drop-idc-says-2024-04-15/</link><description>研究公司 IDC 周日的数据显示，由于争夺第一名的 Android 智能手机制造商的竞争加剧，苹果智能手机出货量在 2024 年第一季度下降了约 10%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 01:54:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-loses-top-phonemaker-spot-samsung-iphone-shipments-drop-idc-says-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>万科称面临短期流动性压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vanke-says-it-faces-short-term-liquidity-pressure-2024-04-15/</link><description>有政府支持的万科表示，该公司面临短期流动性压力和经营困难，但补充称，该公司已准备好“一揽子计划”来稳定业务并削减债务。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 01:37:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vanke-says-it-faces-short-term-liquidity-pressure-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国银行维持政策利率不变，从银行体系中抽走现金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-keeps-policy-rate-unchanged-drains-cash-banking-system-2024-04-15/</link><description>中国央行周一在到期中期贷款展期时，按照普遍预期维持关键政策利率不变，并通过债券工具从银行体系中抽走部分现金。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 01:34:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-keeps-policy-rate-unchanged-drains-cash-banking-system-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚警方称悉尼持刀袭击者可能以女性为目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-police-say-sydney-knife-attacker-may-have-targeted-women-2024-04-15/</link><description>澳大利亚警方周一表示，在悉尼海滩郊区邦迪一个繁忙的购物中心刺死六人的袭击者可能以女性为目标，全国哀悼遇难者，数百人在现场附近献花。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-police-say-sydney-knife-attacker-may-have-targeted-women-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国降息预期减弱，美元走高，日元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-stands-tall-us-rate-cut-bets-recede-2024-04-15/</link><description>美元周一企稳，守住2022年以来最大单周涨幅，因中东冲突升级以及美国利率居高不下的前景提供支撑。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-stands-tall-us-rate-cut-bets-recede-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>创纪录的债务成本意味着气候支出可能会将各国推向破产边缘</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/record-debt-costs-mean-climate-spending-could-push-nations-brink-insolvency-2024-04-15/</link><description>波士顿大学牵头发布的一份报告显示，今年新兴国家将支付创纪录的 4000 亿美元来偿还外债，近 40 个国家在未来五年内无法在不冒违约风险的情况下花费气候适应和可持续发展所需的资金。国际货币基金组织/世界银行春季会议前夕。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:03:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/record-debt-costs-mean-climate-spending-could-push-nations-brink-insolvency-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>中东冲突引发安全热潮，亚洲股市下滑，金价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-14/</link><description>周一，亚洲股市暴跌，金价上涨，因伊朗对以色列的报复性袭击引发了对更广泛地区冲突的担忧，令交易员紧张不安，风险情绪受到打击。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 23:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-14/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着中东紧张局势升级，去风险、寻求安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-14/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 21:47:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-14/</guid></item><item><title>西班牙制药商 Grifols 董事长告诉报纸，将聘请独立董事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/spanish-drug-maker-grifols-will-bring-independent-directors-chairman-tells-2024-04-14/</link><description>西班牙制药商 Grifols 董事长在周日发表的报纸采访中表示，该公司正与今年股价暴跌作斗争，计划在其审计和薪酬委员会中增加独立董事，以改善其治理。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 11:16:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/spanish-drug-maker-grifols-will-bring-independent-directors-chairman-tells-2024-04-14/</guid></item><item><title>佩雷拉击败希尔卫冕UFC轻重量级冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/pereira-knocks-out-hill-retain-ufc-light-heavyweight-title-2024-04-14/</link><description>周六晚，巴西选手亚历克斯·佩雷拉在首轮淘汰赛中击败贾马哈·希尔，卫冕 UFC 轻重量级冠军，而张伟丽则在周六晚的 UFC 300 比赛中击败严晓楠，卫冕平量级腰带。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 06:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/pereira-knocks-out-hill-retain-ufc-light-heavyweight-title-2024-04-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国对伊朗袭击以色列后局势升级“深感担忧”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/china-deeply-concerned-about-escalation-after-iran-strikes-israel-2024-04-14/</link><description>外交部发言人周日表示，伊朗发射无人机和导弹对以色列进行报复性打击后，中东紧张局势升级“深表关切”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 04:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/china-deeply-concerned-about-escalation-after-iran-strikes-israel-2024-04-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来敦促在紧张局势中开放美国言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-maker-nio-urges-openness-us-speech-amid-tensions-2024-04-14/</link><description>中国电动汽车（EV）制造商蔚来创始人在美国罕见的一次演讲中呼吁开放，美国政界人士一直在寻求进一步限制中国进入全球第二大汽车市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 03:59:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-maker-nio-urges-openness-us-speech-amid-tensions-2024-04-14/</guid></item><item><title>肖尔茨警告伊朗，因为对以色列的袭击给中国之行蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/germanys-scholz-kicks-off-china-trip-amid-tensions-over-evs-russia-2024-04-14/</link><description>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨周日警告伊朗不要对以色列发动进一步袭击，因为中东冲突不断升级给他为期三天的中国之行的开始蒙上了阴影。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 02:51:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/germanys-scholz-kicks-off-china-trip-amid-tensions-over-evs-russia-2024-04-14/</guid></item><item><title>朝中社称，朝鲜金正恩将与中国发展长期关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-develop-long-standing-ties-with-china-kcna-says-2024-04-13/</link><description>朝鲜官方媒体朝中社周日援引金正恩与中国最高立法委员赵乐际会面的消息称，朝鲜领导人金正恩重申了与中国发展长期关系的立场。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 21:46:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-develop-long-standing-ties-with-china-kcna-says-2024-04-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国助理国务卿克里滕布林克将于4月14日至16日访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-assistant-secretary-state-kritenbrink-visit-china-april-14-16-2024-04-13/</link><description>美国国务院表示，美国负责东亚事务的最高外交官将于周日开始访问中国，就在几天前，乔·拜登总统与日本和菲律宾领导人举行了峰会，重点讨论了中国在南海的侵略行为。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 14:37:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-assistant-secretary-state-kritenbrink-visit-china-april-14-16-2024-04-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>